                <p class="text">
                    This is the only one capsule hostel in&nbsp;a&nbsp;real&nbsp;double-decker&nbsp;bus around the world. Bagpackers and&nbsp;tourists friendly, also&nbsp;suitable for&nbsp;students and&nbsp;workers.<br /><br />
                </p>
